                            <comment id="13103711" author="tlipcon" created="Tue, 13 Sep 2011 15:56:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think the issue is that items are added to the &lt;tt&gt;tasks&lt;/tt&gt; list without synchronization. So the ArrayList can get into an inconsistent state where iterating it returns null.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13120580" author="stack" created="Tue, 4 Oct 2011 23:26:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This seems reasonable.  All other accesses on tasks are synchronized on this.  +1.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13121633" author="tlipcon" created="Thu, 6 Oct 2011 00:40:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed for 92 and trunk&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13121687" author="hudson" created="Thu, 6 Oct 2011 02:57:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in HBase-0.92 #47 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/HBase-0.92/47/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/HBase-0.92/47/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
